text: Leoš Škoda (born 1 May 1953) is a Czech ski jumper. He competed at the 1972 Winter Olympics and the 1980 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1980 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Liberec
